data.description: Stunning home sitting on the perfect lot for everything you need. Updated and ready for its new owner- Come make it yours. This home offers three bedrooms, two bathrooms on the main level. The primary bedroom has an en suite and also walks out to the composite deck with a hot tub. Overlooking your large, private backyard. Great size, updated kitchen with hardwood flooring features under and over-lit cabinets. The dining area connects to the living room with wood burning fireplace and the great room with vaulted ceilings, floor to ceiling windows, built-ins surround the propane fireplace. Which also walks out to the deck, fully fenced in backyard and above ground pool. Lower level features a finished laundry room, half bath, a living area with tons closets and sink area - in law potential. Access to the attached two car garage. Central air throughout, mini split cooling/heat pumps. Over an acre of land and privacy, fruit trees just complete this property in this desirable neighborhood.
